quran[135]{c,v,t}:
  20,1,"Taa Haa."
  20,2,"Min Telliniraani Alqur'aanaare nde e maa…óa fii yo a tampu."
  20,3,"Si wonaa waaju wonan'de on kuloowo [Alla]."
  20,4,"Ko Jippinaande immorde e oon tak…óo leydi ndi e kammuuji toowu…ói …óin."
  20,5,"Jurmotoo…ó o O fotii e dow Arsi he."
  20,6,"No woodani mo o ko woni ko e kammuuji …óin e ko woni kon e leydi ndi e ko wini kon hakkunde majji kannji …ói…ói e ko woni ko e les leydi."
  20,7,"Si a fen√Īinii konngol ngol, pellet, KaŇčko homo Anndi ko fee√Īi e ko o suu…ói."
  20,8,"Alla dewetee…óo alaa si wonaa KaŇčko, no woodani mo In…óe mo∆ī∆īe …óe."
  20,9,"taw si arii e maa…óa yewtere fii Muusaa."
  20,10,"Tuma nde o yi'inoo yiite, o wi'ani …ďeynguure makko nden: ""√Ďii…ďee, min de mi haynike jayngol mbele-jo'o mi addanat on immorde e maggol docotal ma mi tawa ka [moggo] yiite tinndinoowo."
  20,11,"Tuma nde o aunoo e maggol o noddaa; ""eyma Muusaa""."
  20,12,"[Alla Daalano mo] Min dey ko miin Woni Joomi maa…óa poortu pa…óe maa …óen; pellet an, ha…óa ka aynde(caatngol) Tuwaa La…ď…ďinaande(seninangol)."
  20,13,"Miin mi Su…ďike ma Jento ko wonaa Wahyineede ko."
  20,14,"Pellet, ko miinn Woni Alla dewetee…óo alaa si wonaa miin n rewam; √Īii…ďi e Juulde nde fii Annditugol am."
  20,15,"Pellet, Darnga ko aroowa Mi…óo …óe…ďa suu…óude ngo fii yo…ďe kala woŇčkii ko ki gollu no."
  20,16,"Wota faddo ma e gaayi maggal on mo gooŇč- …óinaani ngo o jokki mbelee…óe makko o halkii."
  20,17,"Ko hol…óuum woni ka √Īaamo maa…óa an Muusaa?"
  20,18,"O maaki: ""Ndu ko tuggordu am mi…óo tuggoo ndu mi…óo liwtirana ndu dammi am …óin, mi…óo mari kadi haajuuji g…ó…ói e mayru""."
  20,19,"O Daali: ""weddo ndu, aan Muusaa""."
  20,20,"O weddi ndu, tawi kayru ko ndu mboo…ódi won'ndi e yahde."
  20,21,"O Daali: ""Nanngu ndi wota a hul min ngartira ndu e mba'adi mayru araniri ndi""."
  20,22,"Naatnu junngo maa…óa ngo ka ndeer seŇčgo maa; ngo yalta ko ngo raneewo ko aldaa e rafi …óum ko Aaya goo."
  20,23,"Fii yo min n kollle immorde e aayeeje amen aaw…óe …óe."
  20,24,"Yah to Fir'awna, pellet, kaŇčko o bewi."
  20,25,"O maaki: ""Jooma Yaacnanam …ďernde am nde."
  20,26,"Newinana am fiyaake am on."
  20,27,"Pi…ďtaa fi…ďnde nde e …óemngal am."
  20,28,"Fii yoo …ďe pahmu konngol am ngol."
  20,29,"Mba…óanaa kam ballo jeyaa…óo ka …ďeynguure am."
  20,30,"[Hara ko] Haaruuna musi…ó…óo am o."
  20,31,"Semmbinir mo darnde am."
  20,32,"Tawnaa mo e ndeer fiyaake am o."
  20,33,"Fii yo mon cenine ko herwi."
  20,34,"Min jaŇčtomaa ko heewi."
  20,35,"Pellet, aan a wonii kumpitii…óo min ."
  20,36,"O Daali: ""GooŇč…óii a okkaama toraare maa…óa nde aan Muusaa""."
  20,37,"GooŇč…óii n neeminiino ma e laawol go…óngol."
  20,38,"Tuma de min mbahayinnoo fa'ade e yumma maa ko wahayinaa ko."
  20,39,"[Men Daali] weddo mo to ndeer hontoore weddo …óum nde kadi ka ndeer diidere, yo diidere nden kadi weddoyo mo ka maayo ; ∆īetta mo ga√Īo am e ga√Īo makko, mi werni e maa…óa Giggol immorde ka am e fii yo a ne'e e dow ndeenka am."
  20,40,"Tuma de banndiraawo maa…óa on yahynoo; o wi'a: ""Enee, yo mi tinndin on e on mo no ne'a mo?"" min ngartirmaa ka yumma maa…óa fii yo gite makko …óen …ďuu…ďu hara o sunaaki. Mbar…óaa woŇčkii min nda…óumaa immorde e sa…óteende nde, min njarribimaa jarrabuyeeje √Īii…ď…óaa duu…ďi ka yim…ďe Madyana refti ngar…óaa ka fodoore aan Muusaa."
  20,41,"Miin su…ďimaa fii hooram"
  20,42,"Yah aan e musi…ó…óo maa on won'dude e aayeeje am …óe wota on derfu e jaŇčtagol Lam."
  20,43,"Njehee ka Fir'awna, pellet, kaŇčko o bewi."
  20,44,"Mbianee mo konngol newiingol mbele-jo'o kaŇčko o waajitoto ma o hula."
  20,45,"∆Āe maaki: ""Joomi amen, minen dey mo…óen kuli nde murtata e hoore amen maa de o bewata""."
  20,46,"O Daali: ""Wota on kule, pellet, miin mi…óo won'di e moo…óon mi…óo Nana Mi…óo Yi'a""."
  20,47,"Ngare ee e makko, mbi'on: ""minen ko min Nulaa…ďe Joomi maa…óa, accit won'dude e amen …ďi…ó…ďe Israa'iila …ďe wota a leptu …ďe, gooŇč…óii min ngddanii e ma aaya immorde ka Joomi maa…óa, kisal wonii e oon jokku…óo Peewal ngal."
  20,48,"GooŇč…óii Wahayinaama e amen; won'dema, Lepte …óe no fawii ka jennu…óo …óuurni."
  20,49,"[Fir'awna] wi'i: ""eeyma o Muusaa, ko hommbo woni Joomi moo…óon?"""
  20,50,"[Muusaa] maaki: ""Joomi amen, ko on Okku…óo kala hu'unde tagoore mayre refti o feewni."
  20,51,"[Fir'awna] wi'i: ""Ko holno gire arane …óen pewndori?"""
  20,52,"[Muusaa] maaki: ""ganndal …óum no ka Joomi am e ndeer Deftere, Joomi am majjataa o yejjitataa""."
  20,53,"Oon ba…óan…óo on leydi ndi we∆ī∆īitaandi, o naadani on e ndeer mayri laabi, O jippini immorde e kammu ngu ndiyam Min njaltiniri …óam nooneeji immorde e pu…ói ceertu…ói."
  20,54,"√Ďaamee ngaynon neemoraa…ói mo'on …ói. Pellet, no e ndeer …óum [ko jaŇčtaa …óoo] Aayeeje fii joomiraa- …ďe kakkillaaji …óin."
  20,55,"Ko immorde e mayri Min Tagi on, ko e ndeer mayri Min nduttata on, ko immorde e mayri kadi Min njaltinoyta on laawol go…ógol"
  20,56,"GooŇč…óii Min kolli mo aayeeje Amen …óen kala majje, o jeddi i o salii."
  20,57,"[Fir'awna] wi'i: ""enee, a ar ka amen fii yo a njaltinir min ka leydi amen mbilewu maa…óa ngun aan Muusaa?"""
  20,58,"Maa min ngaddane mbilewu yeru maggu, wa…ó fodoore hakkunde amen e maa…óa hara men lunndataako nde wonaa an kadi [lunndotoo nde] e nokkuure fotondirnde."
  20,59,"[Muusaa] maaki: fodoore moo…óon nden ko √Īande sa…ó…óugol ngol, yo yim…ďe …ďen moo…ďindire mbeetaa(fenynyaange)."
  20,60,"Fir'awna ruŇčiti o moo…ďi pewje makko …óen refti o ari."
  20,61,"Muusaa maakani …ďe: ""On boniraama, wota on 'pekindo fenaande fawon e Alla sakko O mehira on Lepte, gooŇč…óii sooyii on pekindii…óo."
  20,62,"∆Āe poo…óondiri fiyaake ma…ď…ďe on hakkunde ma…ď…ďe, …ďe vuu…ói cowndi …óin."
  20,63,"∆Āe mbi'i: ""Pellet …ďee …ói…óo ko wilee…ďe he…ďe paalaa yaltinirnde on ka leydi mon e mbilaaku ma…ď…ďe ngu …ďe itta laawol mon …ďurngol l ngol."
  20,64,"Moo…ďitee pewje mo'on …óe refti ngaron ko on lappol, gooŇč…óii malaama hannde on pool…óo."
  20,65,"Muusaa maaki: ""Ko si tawii ko onon mbeddotoo ma si ko minen ngonata adotoo…ďe weddaade.""."
  20,66,"[Muusaa] maaki: ""ko woni, (mbedde), tawi …ďoggi ma…ď…ďe e cawoy ma…ď…ďe koy no wa'itana mo sabu mbilewu ma…ď…ďe ngun woni ko e yahde."
  20,67,"Muusaa so'i kulol ka woŇčkii makko."
  20,68,"Min Daali: 'Wota a hul, pellet ko an woni pooloowo on."
  20,69,"Weddo ko woni ko ka √Īaamo maa…óa …óum mo…óay ko …ďe mo∆ī∆īini ko, pellet, ko …ďe mo∆ī∆īini ko ko pewje mbile bileejo on maletaake nukkuwoo ka o ardi."
  20,70,"Wilee…ďe …ďe mbernaa ko …ďe sujju…ďe, …ďe mbi'i: ""Min ngooŇč…óinii Joomi Haaruuna e Muusaa""."
  20,71,"[Fir'awna] wi'i: Eyoo, on gooŇč…óinii mo ko adii mi duŇčanaade(sakkitaade) on? Pelet, ko kaŇčko woni maw…óo mo'on on anndin…óo on mbilewu ngu, mi woo…óndii, maa mi ta∆īa juu…óe mon …óen e koy…óe mon …óen ta∆īa luutindira, maa mi feta on e julle tama aray anndon ko hommbo e amen …ďuri lepte ca…ótu…óe e heddotoo…óe."
  20,72,"[wilee…ďe …ďe] mbi'i: ""Min …ďurnataa ma e dow koo ko ari e amen immorde e …ďannganguyeeji, e On Tak…óo min, [an Fir'awna] √Īaawu ko √Īaawataa ko, pellet, ko √Īaawataa ko ka ngurndan aduna …óoo""."
  20,73,"Minen dey, men ngooŇč…óinii Joomi amen fii yo o yawtan men goopi amen e kon ko doolu…óaa men e mu'un immorde e mbilewu nguyn, ko Alla woni Mo∆ī∆īo keddotoo…óo."
  20,74,"Pellet on mo ari ka Joomi mu'un hara ko o bon…óo; haray pellet, no woodani mo Jahannama o maayataa e nder magge o wuurataa kadi ."
  20,75,"mo ari ka makko ko o gooŇč…óin…óo hara gooŇč…óii o golliino mo∆ī∆īi …ói, haray …ďen …óon no woodani …ďe Darjaaji Toow…ói …óin."
  20,76,"Aljannaaji √Īii…ďal no doga e ley majji caatli …ói, ko …ďe duumotoo…ďe ndeer ton, ko …óum woni njo…ďdi on la…ď…ďinii…óo."
  20,77,"Goo…óii Min mbahaynii fa'ade e Muusaa ro∆īdu e jeyaa…ďe Am …ďe wa…óan …ďe laawol yooru ngol ka maayo joorngol wota a hul hewtiteede wota a hul [yoolagol]."
  20,78,"Fir'awna jokkitiri …ďe konooli makko …ói, suumi …ďe ka maayo ko suumi …ďe kon."
  20,79,"Fir'awnan majjini yim…ďe makko …ďe, o fewnaani […ďe]."
  20,80,"Eey mon…ďi…ó…ďe Israa'iila gooŇč…óii Min danndiino on e ga√Īo mon on, Min podi on kadi ka baŇčŇče √Īaamo [fello] Tuuri ngon, Min njippini e moo…óon Manna= …óacce njumri e doobe ."
  20,81,"√Ďaamee immorde e laa…ď…ói ko Min arsiki on kon, wota on bew e nder mu'un sakko Tikkere Am nden njippo e mo'on, on mo tikkere am jippii e mu'un gooŇč…óii haray o halkike."
  20,82,"Pellet, Min ko Mi keewu…óo Yawtanngol wonan'de on tuubu…óo o gooŇč…óini o golli ko mo∆ī∆īi refti o feewi."
  20,83,"Ko hol…óum he√Īinmaa ga yim…ďe maa …ďen aan Muusaa?"
  20,84,"[Muusaa] maaki: ""∆Āee…óoo, hie…ďe iwtiri …ďaawo am, mi he√Īike ka Maa…óa Joomi fii yo A welto."
  20,85,"[Alla] Daali: ""Pellet, Mennen gooŇč…óii Men njarribike=finninii yim…ďe maa…óa …ďen …ďaawo maa…óa, Saamiriiyu majjinii …ďe""."
  20,86,"Muusaa ruttii ka yim…ďe makko …ďen ko o tikku…óo sunii…óo; o maaki: ""Ko onon yo yim…ďe, enee, Joomi mo'on Fodanaani on Fodoore Mo∆ī∆īere, kaa ko aadi ndin juutani on? Kaa on faandi nde jippotoo e mo'on Tikkere immorde ka Joomi moo…óon si lunndi …óon fodoore am nden?"""
  20,87,"∆Āe mbi'i: ""Min lunndaaki fodoore maa…óa nde e sago amen, kono minen men ndonndinaama teddeendi e cu…óaaje yim…ďe …ďen men wernii …óe, ko nii Saamiriiyu kadi welirni""."
  20,88,"O yaltinani …ďe …ďanndu ngaari marn hito= huunaango, …ďe mbi'i: ""Ko ko'ol woni dewetee…óo mon e dewetee…óo Muusaa on, o yejjiti [mo …óoo]""."
  20,89,"Enee, …ďee yiaani wonan'dema ruttataako e ma…ď…ďe konngol, ndi maranaa …ďe kadi lorra wonaa fii non [poo…óugol] nafa."
  20,90,"Goo…óii Haaruuna maakaniino …ďe ko adii: ""Ko onon yo yim…ďe, pellet, on njarribora kol, pellet, Joomi moo…óon ko jurmotoo…óo o jokkee kam …óofto…óon yamiroore am nden""."
  20,91,"∆Āe mbi'i i: ""Min ceerataa ko min √Īii…ďu…ďe e [dewal] makkol haa Muusaa ruttoo e amen""."
  20,92,"[Muusaa] maaki: ""eeyma Haaruuna, nde nji'i…óaa …ďe majjii ko ha…ómaa,"
  20,93,"de njokkitataa mi? Kaa a yeddii yamirooe am on?!"""
  20,94,"[Haaruuna] maaki: ""eeyma …ďiy neene am, wota a nanngu wahre am nde wonaa hoore am nden kadi, miin dey, mi hulu wata a wi'i: Mi seerdii hakkunde …ďi…ó…ďe Israa'iila …ďe, mi he…óaaki konngol maa…óa ngol""."
  20,95,"[Muusaa] maaki: ""Ko hol …óuum woni fiyaake maa…óa on an Saamiriiyu?"""
  20,96,"[Saamiriiyu] wi'i: ""Mi yi'ii ko …ďe yiaani …óum, mi nokki nokkannde e batte nulaa…óo on [Jibriila] mi wernii …óum ko nii su…óirani lam woŇčkii am."
  20,97,"[Muusaa] maaki: ""Yahu, pellet, no woodanmaa ka ngurndam nde wowlataa wanaa meemondiral, pellet, no woodanmaa kadi Fodoore a lunndataako nde, ndaarii fa'ade e dewtee…óo maa, on mo √Īallu…óaa ufinaade e hoore mun, mi woondii mi sumat mo refti mi ∆īaroo mo ka maayo e ∆īaragol""."
  20,98,"Pellet, dewetee…óo mon On ko Alla, On Mo Dewetee…óo alaa si wanaa KaŇčko, Ganndal makko Yaajanii kala hu'unde."
  20,99,"Ko wano nii Men polloranay maa immorde e kumpital ko fe∆ī∆īunoo kon, gooŇč…óii Men ngaddanii ma immorde ka Amen jaŇčta."
  20,100,"Mo …óuurike e mayre pellet, o ronndoto √Ďande Darngal teddeele [bakkaatu]."
  20,101,"Ko o luttintee…óo e ndeer majje, bonanii …ďe donngal √Ďande Darngal."
  20,102,"√Ďaande wuttoytee ka alaadu Min moo…ďa bon…ďe …ďen nden √Ďalnde ko mbulii…ďe [gite]."
  20,103,"He…ďe sowndondira hakkunde ma…ď…ďe […ďe mbi'a] on √Īii…ďaani si wonaa [bal…óe] sappo."
  20,104,"Ko Minen ngoni Anndu…ďe ko …ďe wowlata kon, tuma nde koohoo…ďe ma…ď…ďe e laawol wi'ata: ""On √Īii…ďaani si wonaa √Īallal""."
  20,105,"He…ďe lanndaade ma fii pelle …óen, maaku: ""Joomi am ∆īaroto …óe e ∆īaragol""."
  20,106,"O acca [leydi] ndi ko ndi boowal …ďowrungal."
  20,107,"A yi'ataa e mayri oo√Īannde wonaa tintiire.(na…óde)."
  20,108,"Ko nden √Ďande …ďe njokkata noddoowo on ko aldaa e celugol mo,, hitooji …ói yankinanoo Hinnorante On hara a nanataa si wnaa √Īu'umbaangol."
  20,109,"Nden √Ďande tefoore nden nafataa, si wonaa on mo Hinnorante On sakkiti …óum O weltori konngol makko."
  20,110,"Homo Anndi ko woni ko yeeso ma…ď…ďe e …ďaawo ma…ď…ďe …ďe ku…ďindortaa …óum ganndal."
  20,111,"Je'ece …óen yankinanii guru…óo Dartii…óo On, gooŇč…óii sooyii on donndii…óo too√Īe."
  20,112,"On mo ngolli immorde e mo∆ī∆īi …óin hara ko o gooŇč…óin…óo o hulaa too√Īe wonaa uytaneede kadi."
  20,113,"Ko nii Min Telliniri nde Alqur'aanaare Aarabuure Men fensiti kadi e nder mayre immorde e kammbaaji …óin mbela-jo'o kam…ďe …ďe kulat maa nde fu…ó…óanoo …ďe waaju."
  20,114,"Alla Laam…óo Goongu…óo On Toowii, wata a he√Īor Alqur'aanaare nden ko adii nde timmintee e maa…óa wahayu mayre, maaku: ""Joomi …ďeydanam Ganndal""."
  20,115,"GooŇč…óii min ngaadondiri e Aadama ko adii o yejjiti Min ke…ďanaani mo pellital."
  20,116,"Tuma Nde Men Daalannoo maleylaaji …ói cujjanee Aadama, …ďe cujji si wanaa Ibliisa o salii."
  20,117,"Men Daali: ""eeyma Aadama, pellet, oo…óoo ko o ga√Īo maa aan e sonnaajo maa on, wota o yaltin on dey ka Aljanna sakko tampaa""."
  20,118,"Pellet, no woodanmaa nde a heegetaake nder ton a holataa kadi."
  20,119,"Pellet, an a …óom…óetaake nde ton e wuletaake kadi."
  20,120,"Seytaane sonwonsini faade e makko; o wi'i: eeyma Aadama,hara yo mi tinndine e leggal luttineede ngal e laamu ngu follotaako ngu?"""
  20,121,"∆Āe √Īaami e maggal, fee√Īani …ďe mettefooji ma…ď…ďe …óin, …ďe naati e suddirgol e dow ma…ď…ďe immorde e kaaki Aljanna o, Aadama yeddi Joomi makko o majji."
  20,122,"Refti Joomi makko Su…ďii mo, o Tuubini mo o Feewni [mo]."
  20,123,"O Daali: ""njippee toon, onon fof yoga e mo'on ko a√Ī…ďe yoga. Si tawii tun aroyii e mo'on immorde e am peewnoowo kala jokku…óo Peewal Am ngal o majjataa o malkisataake kadi""."
  20,124,"Kala …óurnii…óo gaayi jaŇčtagol lam, haray pellet, no woodani mo ngurndam …ďillu…óam Men moo…ďoya mo √Ďalnde Darngal ko o bum…óo."
  20,125,"O wi'a: ""Joomi, ko fii hol…óum moo…ďan…óaa lam ko mi bum…óo, goŇč…óii mi laatinoke ji'oowo?"""
  20,126,"O Daala: ""Ko wano nii arnoo e maa…óa Aayeeje Amen …óen njejjitu…óaa …óe, ko wano nii kadi hannde njejjitirte…óaa""."
  20,127,"Ko wano nii min njo…ďirta on …ďurtin…óo …óo o gooŇč…óinaa aayeeje Joomi makko …óen, pellet, ko Lepte Laakara …óen …ďuri sa…ótude ko …óen kadi heddotoo."
  20,128,"Kaa hara …ďannganaali …ďe no foti hewde ko Men halki ado ma…ď…ďe immorde e gire? He…ďe yaha e ko…óooli ma…ď…ďe, pellet, no e …óuum aayeeje wonan'de joomiraa…ďe kakkillaaji …ďen."
  20,129,"Sinno wonaano Daalol aditii ngol immorde ka Joomi maa…óa [Lepte] …óen laatotono duumii…óe e lajal innaangal."
  20,130,"Mun√Īo e dow ko …ďe kaalata ko, subuhinor jettugol Joomi maa…óa ko adii ∆īellitagol naange ngen e ko adii mutugol magge e ka saa'iiji jemma subuhino e ka seraaji √Īallal belajo'o a weltoto."
  20,131,"Wota a yawtin de gite maa …óe fa'ade k ko Min ndakmini …óum nooneeji immorde e ma…ď…ďe, cu…óaari ngurndam aduna fii yo Min njarribor …ďe e …óum, Arsike Joomi maa…óa on …ďuri mo∆ī∆īude ko on kadi keddotoo."
  20,132,"Yamir …ďeynguure maa…óa nden Juulde nden mun√Īitoraa e …óum, Min la…ďndaaki ma arsike ko Minen arsikaymaa. Battane [mo∆ī∆īe] …óen kadi wonanii huloo…ďe Alla …ďen."
  20,133,"∆Āe mbi'i'i: ""Ko h…ónno ara e amen Aaya immorde ka Joomi makko?"" Enee, hara araani e ma…ď…ďe …ďanngal ko woni ko e …óeri adani …óin?"
  20,134,"Sinndo Minen Min kalkirno …ďe Lepte ko adii …óum, …ďe mbi'atno: ""Joomi amen, ko hannoo Nualaa e amen Nulaa…óo men njokka Aayeeje Maa …óen, ko adii nde Men koyata men hesra."
  20,135,"Maaku: ""Gooto kala [e amen] no habbitii, [onon kadi] habbitee aray anndon ko hommbo woni jom Laawol Pocciingol ngol ko hommbo kadi feewi""."
